{
  "name": "Capital Project Selection (300 projects)",
  "domain": "corporate finance",
  "context": "Choose which of 300 capital projects to fund this cycle to maximize NPV and strategic fit while holding down spend and portfolio risk, under a hard $1550M budget, per-category caps, enabler dependencies, and mutually-exclusive bets. At this scale the efficient frontier is large and irregular \u2014 an exact MILP per scalarization resolves it densely where a fixed-resolution metaheuristic leaves coverage gaps.",
